| If the question says...                      | Think...                                          |
| -------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| Take or don't take each element once         | **0/1 Knapsack**                                  |
| Unlimited copies of an item                  | **Unbounded Knapsack**                            |
| Can we make a target sum?                    | **Subset Sum (0/1 Knapsack)**                     |
| Count ways to make a sum                     | **Count Subset / Coin Change** (depends on reuse) |
| Maximize profit with a capacity              | **Knapsack**                                      |
| Two strings or arrays, find something common | **LCS**                                           |
| One array, increasing/decreasing sequence    | **LIS**                                           |
| Grid with movement constraints               | **Grid DP**                                       |
| Split/cut an interval optimally              | **Interval DP**                                   |
| Visit every node/subset                      | **Bitmask DP**                                    |
| Count numbers with digit constraints         | **Digit DP**                                      |


